or hatred.

913
01:00:09.880 --> 01:00:11.400
But this thing
could be responsible

914
01:00:11.440 --> 01:00:13.440
for the death of
I don't know how many women.

915
01:00:13.520 --> 01:00:16.000
Every attack. every unleashing

916
